0.4-SNAPSHOT

 - Bug Fix: Missing # in links
 - Bug Fix: Error no longer caused by WordPress passing an empty $atts
 - Add title text to citations

0.3

 - Switch to class architecture
 - Add flag for treating Notes and Citations separately
 - Using backref no longer causes duplicate ids
 - Each use of backref generates an extra up arrow in the entry

0.2

 - Support for blank citations (show as 'citation needed')
 - Add support for supplementary content in citations
 - Citation links have the rel="cite" property
 - BUGFIX: Backrefs now look up the name correctly
